annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 8  Areas no longer used for production purposes, subject to the payment of subsidies, and area subject to set-aside incentive schemes, broken down by:
annotations.translation: 8 不再用于生产目的、须支付补贴的地区，以及须预留奖励计划的地区，细分为：

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: (a) areas no longer used for production purposes, subject to the payment of subsidies (already recorded under D/22 and F/3)
annotations.translation: (a) 不再用于生产目的、需支付补贴的地区（已在 D/22 和 F/3 项下记录）

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: (b) areas used for the production of agricultural raw material for non-food purposes (e.g. sugar beet, rape, non-forestry trees and bushes etc., including lentils, chick peas and vetches; already recorded under D and G)
annotations.translation: (b) 用于生产非粮食用途农业原料的地区（例如甜菜、油菜、非林业树木和灌木等，包括扁豆、鹰嘴豆和野豌豆；已在 D 和 G 项下记录）

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: areas converted into permanent pasture and meadow ( already recorded under F / 1 and F / 2 ) ( ¹ )
annotations.translation: 改建为永久牧场和草地的地区（已在 F/1 和 F/2 项下记录）(¹)

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: (d) former agricultural areas converted into wooded area or being prepared for afforestation (already recorded under H/2) (¹)
annotations.translation: (d) 原农业区改为林区或准备造林（已在 H/2 项下记录）(¹)

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: (e) other areas (already recorded under H/1 and H/3) (¹)
annotations.translation: (e) 其他区域（已在 H/1 和 H/3 项下记录）(¹)

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: J. Livestock (on the reference day of the survey)

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 2. Bovine animals, under one year old, male and female
annotations.translation: 2. 牛类动物，一岁以下，雄性和雌性

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 3. Male bovine animals, one but less than two years old
annotations.translation: 3. 雄性牛类动物，一岁以上两岁以下

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 4. Female bovine animals, one but less than two years old
annotations.translation: 4. 雌性牛类动物，一岁以上两岁以下

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 5. Male bovine animals, two years old and over
annotations.translation: 5. 雄性牛类动物，两岁及以上

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 6. Heifers, two years old and over

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 11. Piglets having a live weight of under 20 Kilograms
annotations.translation: 11. 活体重量在 20 千克以下的小猪

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.text: 12. Breeding sows weighing 50 Kilograms and over
annotations.translation: 12. 体重 50 千克及以上的种母猪

annotations.label: List-item
annotations.translation: (d) 其他地方未提及的其他家禽

annotations.translation: (¹) 德国可合并标题 8(c)、8(d) 和 8(e)。
